headline: 4 Agriculture Operations Stocks to Watch as Trade Uncertainties Weigh
summary: The Agriculture - Operations industry is navigating rising costs and trade pressures while tapping growth in health-focused products and innovation. CTVA, ADM, DOLE and AVO look promising.
